description: A man in his early 40s and a man in his late teens have died and a third man is seriously injured.
title: Glengarriff: Two men die in crash in west County Cork
title_page: Glengarriff: Two men die in crash in west County Cork - BBC News
maintext: The injured man was airlifted to Cork University Hospital, while a forth person who was also in the vehicle was not hurt in the crash.
